contentrichtext.text: {{confuse|diaeresis (disambiguation)}} '''Diuresis''' may refer to: * Urine production, as an aspect of [[fluid balance]] * Excessive urine production - see [[polyuria]] * [[Forced diuresis]], increased urine formation by diuretics and fluid * [[Immersion diuresis]], a type of diuresis caused by immersion of the body in water * [[Osmotic diuresis]], increased urination caused by the presence of substances in the kidneys * [[Rebound diuresis]], sudden resurgence of urine flow that occurs during convalescence from acute renal failure {{disambig}} [[ca:Diüresi]] [[cs:Diuréza]] [[da:Diurese]] [[de:Diurese]] [[fr:Diurèse]] [[it:Diuresi]] [[pl:Diureza]] [[pt:Diurese]] [[ru:Диурез]] [[uk:Діурез]]
